==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uvula
<hw>U"vu*la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., dim of L.
<ets>uva</ets> a grape, the uvula.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The
pendent fleshy lobe in the middle of the posterior border of the soft
palate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The term is also applied to a somewhat similar lobe on
the under side of the cerebellum and to another on the inner surface of
the neck of the bladder.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uvular</ent>⟦br⟧
